cat << EOF
ttyrec is a tty recorder. Recorded data can be played back with the included ttyplay command.
ttyrec is just a derivative of script command for recording timing information with microsecond
accuracy as well. It can record emacs -nw, vi, lynx, or any programs running on tty. 
